re for instructions.'=>'Пожалуйста, прочтите инструкции выше.','Do you like %s?'=>'Вам нравится %s?','Write a review'=>'','Need help?'=>'Требуется помощь?','Members Count:'=>'','Result:'=>'','Test Result:'=>'','Follow %s'=>'Читать %s','Join %s'=>'Добавить %s','Goto %1$s and click/drag %2$s and place it where you want it to be.'=>'','Appearance'=>'','Widgets'=>'','Alternately, you can use the below shortcode or the block available in block editor.'=>'','Inside page or post content:'=>'','Inside the theme templates'=>'','or'=>'','Widget Info'=>'','Please wait…'=>'','Test Token'=>'','Send Test'=>'','Add'=>'','Something went wrong'=>'','Could not connect'=>'','Error:'=>'','A message will be sent to the Channel/Group/Chat. You can modify the text below'=>'','This is a test message'=>'','Success'=>'','Lets fix these errors first.'=>'Давайте сперва исправим эти ошибки.','Changes saved successfully.'=>'Изменения сохранены успешно.','Invalid %s'=>'Недопустимое %s','%s required.'=>'%s (обязательно)','Changes could not be saved.'=>'Изменения не могут быть сохранены.','https://t.me/WPTelegram'=>'','Add comments to posts/pages on your WordPress website by using Telegram Comments Widget.'=>'','WP Socio'=>'','https://wpsocio.com'=>''],'language'=>'ru_RU','x-generator'=>'Poedit 2.4.2'];